channel.title: Project Divine 718 ( New)
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/9ir6uq.jpg[/img] Anyone reading this, Just read the whole post. Project Divine is my new RSPS that i work really hard on. Recently have made it VPS Hosted and is online 24/7. there is not that many players atm maybe 10 online and i know it will grow. I am fixing alot and taking any suggestions into consideration. I code alot, make many updates and fix Any bugs players ask about. If you are interested in the server you could just try it out, no one is forcing you to stay. The forums link is www.pdforums.webs.com and there is a webclient and downloadable link that will be on the bottom. There is a few custom(recolored) items that i think is a nice bonus to the server. I put any donations towards the vps and maybe even a domain. My staff team is great but im always looking for better. There is nice squeal of fortune and nice Xp rates. I know there are alot of servers out there, and mine is not the best. Hope to see you on - Jason Owner of Project Divine
